title: Latvia CPI Transportation
description: The transportation sub-index of the CPI basket in Latvia increased to 139.30 points in October of 2022 from 135.20 points in September of 2022. CPI Transportation in Latvia averaged 91.04 points from 1999 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 144.80 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 55.30 points in February of 1999. This page provides - Latvia Cpi Transportation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistical Bureau of Latvia
